text: Overcome is the debut studio album by English singer Alexandra Burke. It was released 19 October 2009 on Syco Music. It was released a year after Burke won the British talent show, The X Factor. It was also re-released in 2010 with a new artwork and three extra songs. ==Reviews== Overcome has received mainly positive reviews. ==Track listing== Information taken from Overcome liner notes.
